October 20, 2014
Moore-Muñiz joins GMK Associates
GMK Associates Inc., has made Keri L. Moore-Muñiz the senior design manager in the Interiors Division. She will be customizing spaces for senior living and hospitality clients.

Moore-Muñiz was previously at studioSIX5, an Austin, TX-based interior design firm focused on the senior living industry. She has worked on the first LEED-Certified (Silver) senior community in the United States: Timber Ridge at Talus in Issaquah, WA. She also has worked on CCRCs in Texas, Missouri and Arizona.
She received her bachelor's degree from Texas State University.
